data.value:
Mapped Touchpad Area: Sets the mapped touchpad region (0 to 100, 0 = left/top, 100 = right/bottom)
Mapped Screen Area: Sets the mapped screen region (0 to 100, 0 = left/top, 100 = right/bottom)
Mouse smoothing: Sets the touch smoothing factor (0 to 100, 0 for no smoothing) Less smoothing = shaky movement, High smoothing: more input lag
Drawing mode: Enables left clicking by touching the touchpad. Acts kinda like a drawing tablet in this mode.
Please press the reset button after changing setting for them to take effect.
Original program created by Andrew Sun(https://github.com/apsun) GUI created by Derrick Timmermans(https://github.com/LumpBloom7)
